{"tid":520720,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"無法避免 列馬終要變險簽","createTime":"2018-01-05T16:56:51.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-05T21:51:51.000Z","uid":133266,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"b3b00a263b9d6082940347c51e21178cf6b7447f","tid":520720,"uid":133266,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T16:56:51.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">零四那種情形極霸氣</span><br />\n歡眾看著亦會覺得很好奇<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">迷雲從前是道理</span> 就似天使這麼美<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">賣臭燒 賣法比</span> 無限美<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">雲格缺點 就是極熞家只購入幼齒<br />\n時常念記大帝及柏金 當年舊戰積<br />\n回望最初 就是路斯基未能提及過<br />\n人情亦欠奉 偉大退役也不可</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">無法避免 列馬終要變險簽<br />\n利記億貨惹不起纏綿 可算豪門<br />\n但我竟期盼基佬X朗<br />\n而錯判竟可錯過三分</span><br />\n累你失去了冠冕<br />\n但你卻待我一點也不變<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">雲佩斯他 就是極反骨 跟費sir踢波<br />\n淪落地照用托柒韋迫 不能用腦麼<br />\n梅迪殺卡 下滑 或高斯夢遺亦漸老<br />\n門前那間諜確實接撲 那麼多</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">前四漸遠 二五山去踢哥狗<br />\n但奧燒也撐不起病患 冬季無緣</span><br />\n令你這完美天使污染<br />\n而振翅非不到你的天<br />\n累你失去了冠冕<br />\n但你卻待我一點也不變<br />\n<br />\n我亦陪著你這些年<br />\n仍然難敵我心虛<br />\n怎麼算　令你沾上了污點<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">誤判一再惹不起豪門　只惹閒言</span><br />\n令你這完美天使污染<br />\n而振翅非不到你的天<br />\n累你失去了冠冕<br />\n但你卻待我一點也不變"},{"pid":"5bb500cbd9be1c05f2c46d85d424c0dd2f34f237","tid":520720,"uid":133266,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T21:25:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3f03af4b31cf3fa61c1e4a4f19d0a0e25ecfc99","tid":520720,"uid":7729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T21:49:18.000Z","msg":"而錯判竟可錯過三分<br />\n句野好奇怪"},{"pid":"c1b7aac049453f5e458d315634b98db59abd6182","tid":520720,"uid":59678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T21:51:39.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://na.cx/i/148y4E.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F148y4E.jpg&d=vVr%2FWdiuJrFGz5lifNlARW6tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=08155a49\" target=\"_blank\">https://na.cx/i/148y4E.jpg</a>"},{"pid":"42bf0faaf6c945d5bfdc837bbcb22b787207cd14","tid":520720,"uid":59678,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T21:51:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/148y4E.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F148y4E.jpg&h=2c2ecb57&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}